title: A06 SA: Educational status and labour market status for people aged from 16 to 24 (seasonally adjusted)
summary: Educational status and labour market status (employment, unemployment and economic inactivity) of people aged from 16 to 24 (seasonally adjusted). This table shows estimates for people in full-time education and people not in full-time education.
